    "They showcase that nations with low income and internet users are associated with negative sentiment.",
    "Similarly, Sheng et al. (2019) identify gender and racial bias in GPT-2 generated text using \"regard\" as a metric instead of sentiment.",
    "Regard is an improvement over sentiment scores as it measures text polarity towards a demographic rather than overall polarity.",
    "LLMs are used not just for plain text generation, but also to accomplish many other tasks like classification or entailment.",
    "Dev et al. (2020) uncover bias across multiple demographics using entailment task."
